u" data-alchemy-prerendered-component-id="ced0fe8c-c4d8-4f4d-a008-ee2b626171c1">{%- comment -%}replo-liquid-chunk-begin{%- endcomment -%}<div style="width:100%;height:100%" data-alchemy-prerendered-placeholder="true">{% section 'founder-story' %}</div>{%- comment -%}replo-liquid-chunk-end{%- endcomment -%}</div><div data-rid="3f0c3683-7dbf-4145-984c-e249dd03b18c" class="r-13ecl40"><div id="reviews" data-oke-widget=""></div></div><div data-rid="0e8ab663-03b4-4012-a0ec-320d34d94dfb" class="r-i73gm3"><div data-rid="519e0bc8-eb5b-44d4-8f7d-b3d49fd0ea76" class="r-zyko7t"><div data-rid="6f49888a-ec44-4c6e-8a89-b8861e5ab9a3" class="r-1ijyz8p alchemy-rte" style="--replo-library-ae6ad90b-9359-4cab-b761-99dbb2179a44-styles-32eaebe0-5a60-46ca-b9b5-bb2df355112b-attributes-fontsize:40px;--replo-library-ae6ad90b-9359-4cab-b761-99dbb2179a44-styles-32eaebe0-5a60-46ca-b9b5-bb2df355112b-attributes-textdecoration:undefined;--replo-library-ae6ad90b-9359-4cab-b761-99dbb2179a44-styles-32eaebe0-5a60-46ca-b9b5-bb2df355112b-attributes-fontfamily:HelveticaNeueLTPro-Bd;--replo-library-ae6ad90b-9359-4cab-b761-99dbb2179a44-styles-32eaebe0-5a60-46ca-b9b5-bb2df355112b-attributes-fontweight:400;--replo-library-ae6ad90b-9359-4cab-b761-99dbb2179a44-styles-32eaebe0-5a60-46ca-b9b5-bb2df355112b-attributes-lineheight:50px;--replo-library-ae6ad90b-9359-4cab-b761-99dbb2179a44-styles-32eaebe0-5a60-46ca-b9b5-bb2df355112b-attributes-letterspacing:-0.2px;--replo-library-ae6ad90b-9359-4cab-b761-99dbb2179a44-styles-5db417d6-04d0-4c67-8f58-9f136bdc49d2-attributes-fontsize:28px;--replo-library-ae6ad90b-9359-4cab-b761-99dbb2179a44-styles-5db417d6-04d0-4c67-8f58-9f136bdc49d2-attributes-textdecoration:undefined;--replo-library-ae6ad90b-9359-4cab-b761-99dbb2179a44-styles-5db417d6-04d0-4c67-8f58-9f136bdc49d2-attributes-fontfamily:HelveticaNeueLTPro-Bd;--replo-library-ae6ad90b-9359-4cab-b761-99dbb2179a44-styles-5db417d6-04d0-4c67-8f58-9f136bdc49d2-attributes-fontweight:400;--replo-library-ae6ad90b-9359-4cab-b761-99dbb2179a44-styles-5db417d6-04d0-4c67-8f58-9f136bdc49d2-attributes-lineheight:120%;--replo-library-ae6ad90b-9359-4cab-b761-99dbb2179a44-styles-5db417d6-04d0-4c67-8f58-9f136bdc49d2-attributes-letterspacing:-0.4px"><span style="width:100%"><h1>Frequently Asked Questions</h1></span></div><div data-rid="758826ee-80df-4ced-b8e1-25dcd286c768" class="r-1xvdujr" data-orientation="vertical"><div data-rid="5728e561-2652-4f0f-b831-472a01a1f5a7" class="r-r3svg0" data-replo-collapsible="true" data-state="closed" data-orientation="vertical"><div data-rid="4517737d-5f07-4b9c-8858-7e117fe8a2f2" aria-expanded="false" aria-controls="replo-:R1mj2:" tabindex="0" role="button" class="r-1kd8f25"><div data-rid="27b79202-3afb-4acf-8d35-40ec25ff9a4e" class="r-ime4tg alchemy-rte"><span style="width:100%"><p>What if it doesn't work for me?</p></span></div><div data-rid="23463385-d53b-42ee-af34-b259039cd833" class="r-qvkibi" aria-hidden="true"><svg stroke="currentColor" fill="currentColor" stroke-width="0" viewBox="0 0 16 16" role="img" aria-label="Collapse/Expand" style="width:var(--rsw, 100%);height:auto;max-height:100%" class="r-t6m1nc" height="1em" width="1em" xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg"><path d="M8 4a.5.5 0 0 1 .5.5v3h3a.5.5 0 0 1 0 1h-3v3a.5.5 0 0 1-1 0v-3h-3a.5.5 0 0 1 0-1h3v-3A.5.5 0 0 1 8 4"></path></svg></div></div><div class="replo-animated" hidden="" id="replo-:R1mj2:"><div data-rid="bf96fd1c-89d3-4a6d-892e-66d09edde51f" class="r-1otbjl2"><div data-rid="1a1095da-a846-4fc6-a412-688e52f9c784" class="r-sahxdj alchemy-rte"><span style="width:100%"><p>You're covered by our 90-day money-back guarantee on your first order, no questions asked. If you try Rejuvia for a few weeks and don't love it, just email us at <a href="mailto:hello@rejuvia.co">hello@rejuvia.co</a> and we'll refund you. We'd rather earn your trust than hold your money.</p></span></div></div></div></div><div data-rid="655fcfd0-71e0-4d31-a38e-161fc7191077" class="r-uzh77e" data-replo-collapsible="true" data-state="closed" data-orientation="vertical"><div data-rid="dee7c48d-b0c0-4295-85d3-573a98fe8e02" aria-expanded="false" aria-controls="replo-:R2mj2:" tabindex="0" role="button" class="r-1xm9jw3"><div data-rid="cf52fee4-19b1-431c-9eb7-6f263ff5dcbc" class="r-194uda3 alchemy-rte"><span style="width:100%"><p>Will I wake up groggy in the morning?</p></span></div><div data-rid="81f90dd0-5326-4c6a-abb7-24315f2e4ad6" class="r-lw56s8" aria-hidden="true"><svg stroke="currentColor" fill="currentColor" stroke-width="0" viewBox="0 0 16 16" role="img" aria-label="Collapse/Expand" style="width:var(--rsw, 100%);height:auto;max-height:100%" class="r-od02gh" height="1em" width="1em" xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg"><path d="M8 4a.5.5 0 0 1 .5.5v3h3a.5.5 0 0 1 0 1h-3v3a.5.5 0 0 1-1 0v-3h-3a.5.5 0 0 1 0-1h3v-3A.5.5 0 0 1 8 4"></path></svg></div></div><div class="replo-animated" hidden="" id="replo-:R2mj2:"><div data-rid="419f173d-8285-49db-872b-3d0167924f06" class="r-nqql49"><div data-rid="a528cefa-4c83-42a9-ac78-db987c3c302a" class="r-1recs5v alchemy-rte"><span style="width:100%"><p>No, and this is the #1 reason people switch to Rejuvia. We use a low 2mg dose of melatonin (most gummies pack 5-10mg, which is what causes the morning hangover) paired with 12 natural sleep herbs that calm your mind without knocking you out cold. You'll wake up rested, not foggy.</p></span></div></div></div></div><div data-rid="865cbeb3-ea29-4f74-8192-53484c3ecd2a" class="r-sf3rzl" data-replo-collapsible="true" data-state="closed" data-orientation="vertical"><div data-rid="5e6f2ba8-ef65-40e2-8d5a-1eb44efaee68" aria-expanded="false" aria-controls="replo-:R3mj2:" tabindex="0" role="button" class="r-7tjfzy"><div data-rid="1c251378-33d5-4443-a787-82ed8a4080ff" class="r-1so6v2r alchemy-rte"><span style="width:100%"><p>How fast will I feel Rejuvia working?</p></span></div><div data-rid="8c62365c-6e3f-4a40-af28-c2981872807a" class="r-2tkfwg" aria-hidden="true"><svg stroke="currentColor" fill="currentColor" stroke-width="0" viewBox="0 0 16 16" role="img" aria-label="Collapse/Expand" style="width:var(--rsw, 100%);height:auto;max-height:100%" class="r-1dn02lt" height="1em" width="1em" xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg"><path d="M8 4a.5.5 0 0 1 .5.5v3h3a.5.5 0 0 1 0 1h-3v3a.5.5 0 0 1-1 0v-3h-3a.5.5 0 0 1 0-1h3v-3A.5.5 0 0 1 8 4"></path></svg></div></div><div class="replo-animated" hidden="" id="replo-:R3mj2:"><div data-rid="7ab655b5-7039-480c-9eb4-cd82334b323e" class="r-4v7mdx"><div data-rid="b932da24-9a55-415e-99cc-df3962c42e73" class="r-xds0ko alchemy-rte"><span style="width:100%"><p>Most people feel it the first or second night. Because the spray absorbs under your tongue, it skips your stomach completely and gets to work in about 10-15 minutes instead of the 60-90 minutes pills and gummies take. That said, if you've been dealing with bad sleep for years, give it a full 7-10 nights of consistent use. The ingredients build on each other and the deeper, full-night sleep typically kicks in by the end of week one.</p></span></div></div></div></div><div data-rid="4e9e7a78-8124-443e-aa2a-f677a410a3b1" class="r-72izso" data-replo-collapsible="true" data-state="closed" data-orientation="vertical"><div data-rid="afaa335c-ed8c-4838-86a1-6e00c9bbf2ff" aria-expanded="false" aria-controls="replo-:R4mj2:" tabindex="0" role="button" class="r-zb4bl5"><div data-rid="50d06b62-1889-414f-bd51-b8dfbcf06ee2" class="r-1q438i5 alchemy-rte"><span style="width:100%"><p>Is Rejuvia habit-forming? Will I become dependent on it?</p></span></div><div data-rid="a57e67ab-54d7-492e-949b-c32cbbd436ad" class="r-1y6ekfl" aria-hidden="true"><svg stroke="currentColor" fill="currentColor" stroke-width="0" viewBox="0 0 16 16" role="img" aria-label="Collapse/Expand" style="width:var(--rsw, 100%);height:auto;max-height:100%" class="r-ue3b09" height="1em" width="1em" xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg"><path d="M8 4a.5.5 0 0 1 .5.5v3h3a.5.5 0 0 1 0 1h-3v3a.5.5 0 0 1-1 0v-3h-3a.5.5 0 0 1 0-1h3v-3A.5.5 0 0 1 8 4"></path></svg></div></div><div class="replo-animated" hidden="" id="replo-:R4mj2:"><div data-rid="8e5fd62b-220e-437b-8d29-18e7cdfb1895" class="r-1v0wgh2"><div data-rid="35aa346a-47b7-41c6-bf88-07f4a7df8c4e" class="r-6smdf6 alchemy-rte"><span style="width:100%"><p>Not at all. Rejuvia is non-habit-forming, and you can use it every night or only when you need it. Most of our customers use it nightly as part of their wind-down routine because they love how they feel, not because they have to. Plenty of customers also use it 3-4 nights a week or only when travel and stress throw off their sleep.</p></span></div></div></div></div><div data-rid="2732a94e-898a-4f90-b891-dd7cc074e96d" class="r-r6z3eb" data-replo-collapsible="true" data-state="closed" data-orientation="vertical"><div data-rid="aa7cc845-3162-4383-9015-c2db00534bd8" aria-expanded="false" aria-controls="replo-:R5mj2:" tabindex="0" role="button" class="r-1ctytwj"><div data-rid="d31bdb71-265c-4111-aecb-53ea7ea9cbbb" class="r-1kyg0bi alchemy-rte"><span style="width:100%"><p>What are the ingredients in Rejuvia?</p></span></div><div data-rid="ebddd574-1e62-4704-baba-9622d454893c" class="r-5wy5fx" aria-hidden="true"><svg stroke="currentColor" fill="currentColor" stroke-width="0" viewBox="0 0 16 16" role="img" aria-label="Collapse/Expand" style="width:var(--rsw, 100%);height:auto;max-height:100%" class="r-18vd2p3" height="1em" width="1em" xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg"><path d="M8 4a.5.5 0 0 1 .5.5v3h3a.5.5 0 0 1 0 1h-3v3a.5.5 0 0 1-1 0v-3h-3a.5.5 0 0 1 0-1h3v-3A.5.5 0 0 1 8 4"></path></svg></div></div><div class="replo-animated" hidden="" id="replo-:R5mj2:"><div data-rid="c4bd6f69-66db-480c-aa7d-0fa25d3654f2" class="r-11bgcgb"><div data-rid="b10e653f-5a05-49c3-902f-7f68ba3c6765" class="r-1i795hg alchemy-rte"><span style="width:100%"><p>Rejuvia has 13 all-natural ingredients working together: a low 2mg of melatonin, plus 5-HTP, valerian root, passionflower, chamomile, lemon balm, skullcap, magnolia bark, hops, cramp bark, ginkgo biloba, peppermint, and feverfew. That's why it works on falling asleep, staying asleep, and waking up refreshed instead of just one of the three.</p></span></div></div></div></div><div data-rid="617037a4-0692-4b1f-a171-da163e12c062" class="r-10c2q4f" data-replo-collapsible="true" data-state="closed" data-orientation="vertical"><div data-rid="718ca42c-f936-4341-ae6b-0d9a5356691e" aria-expanded="false" aria-controls="replo-:R6mj2:" tabindex="0" role="button" class="r-15td9t5"><div data-rid="1b5a7a0a-d5b5-4fed-a3fb-8af54e3fe469" class="r-1y9zeoe alchemy-rte"><span style="width:100%"><p>What flavor is Rejuvia?</p></span></div><div data-rid="328376a9-668b-47bc-8f5a-94f2f67a1da9" class="r-1fp365i" aria-hidden="true"><svg stroke="currentColor" fill="currentColor" stroke-width="0" viewBox="0 0 16 16" role="img" aria-label="Collapse/Expand" style="width:var(--rsw, 100%);height:auto;max-height:100%" class="r-1stk6wn" height="1em" width="1em" xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg"><path d="M8 4a.5.5 0 0 1 .5.5v3h3a.5.5 0 0 1 0 1h-3v3a.5.5 0 0 1-1 0v-3h-3a.5.5 0 0 1 0-1h3v-3A.5.5 0 0 1 8 4"></path></svg></div></div><div class="replo-animated" hidden="" id="replo-:R6mj2:"><div data-rid="f12e1b93-965c-4889-a647-d36d17f5340a" class="r-4c4wco"><div data-rid="c304e852-94eb-47f0-b9e2-9ea1edc1f78c" class="r-qeepae alchemy-rte"><span style="width:100%"><p>Rejuvia oral sprays have a refreshing, all-natural mint flavoring. It's noticeable and refreshing but mild — if you don't love mint, it's not overpowering.</p></span></div></div></div></div><div data-rid="d8f179b4-35d0-4fe4-a156-ca8742056757" class="r-174qwqx" data-replo-collapsible="true" data-state="closed" data-orientation="vertical"><div data-rid="8ceb5b63-bb41-49bd-ab1f-89ce3d1a43e7" aria-expanded="false" aria-controls="replo-:R7mj2:" tabindex="0" role="button" class="r-h7ch1k"><div data-rid="3ce83460-e054-4b69-b9bc-abcb6a26d642" class="r-e8mqe3 alchemy-rte"><span style="width:100%"><p>Is this a subscription?</p></span></div><div data-rid